                <ul>
                    <li><strong>SUPERIOR STUDIES</strong> : <strong>The</strong> ONMU offers postgraduate studies in all areas of medicine. The duration of the study is 2-3 years.</li>
                    <li><strong>PREMEDICAL COURSE</strong> : This is an intensive Russian program for students who wish to continue their studies at the ONMU or any other university in Ukraine. The duration of the preparatory course is one year. After passing, a diploma is awarded.</li>
                    <li><strong>PREPARATORY DEPARTMENT</strong> : This course is specially designed for foreign students who do not have the necessary conditions to access undergraduate programs. It also helps to enable students to bridge the gap between school and university. <br>
