                <p>The faculty of postdoctoral training offers the study in 50 medical specialties in internship, master's degree and clinical internship. At the Department of the National Medical University of Odessa (ONMU), in addition to traditional teaching methods, there is also a module study. The ever-changing base of IT equipment makes it possible to use modern computer know-how and global computer networks under study.</p>
